---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`About – ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Learn more about the qualifications and experience of Dr Neeraj Purohit, consultant MSK radiologist." />
	</head>
	<body class="bg-slate-50 font-sans text-slate-800 antialiased">
		<header class="top-0 z-50 sticky bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-slate-200 border-b">
			<div class="flex justify-between items-center mx-auto px-4 py-4 max-w-6xl">
				<a href="/" class="font-semibold text-xl">Dr&nbsp;Neeraj&nbsp;Purohit</a>
				<nav class="space-x-6 text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">
					<a href="/" class="hover:text-emerald-600">Home</a>
					<a href="/about" class="font-semibold hover:text-emerald-600">About</a>
					<a href="/info" class="hover:text-emerald-600">Info</a>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>

		<main class="space-y-14 mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-5xl">
			<section>
				<h1 class="mb-6 font-bold text-emerald-700 text-4xl">About&nbsp;Dr&nbsp;Neeraj&nbsp;Purohit</h1>
				<p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">Dr&nbsp;Purohit graduated with honours from Imperial College London and completed specialist radiology training at St Mary's Hospital, followed by a prestigious Musculoskeletal Imaging Fellowship at the Royal National Orthopaedic Hospital.</p>
				<p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">He has held substantive consultant posts within the NHS and now practices <strong>100% privately</strong> at leading centres including The Harley Street Clinic and Wellington Hospital.</p>
				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">In addition to clinical work, Dr&nbsp;Purohit is an invited lecturer for the Royal College of Radiologists, regularly publishes in peer-reviewed journals and acts as imaging advisor to elite sports teams.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-emerald-700 text-3xl">Qualifications &amp; Memberships</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 pl-6 text-lg list-disc">
					<li>MBBS (Hons) – Imperial College London</li>
					<li>FRCR – Fellow of the Royal College of Radiologists</li>
					<li>ESSR – European Society of Musculoskeletal Radiology</li>
					<li>BSSR – British Society of Skeletal Radiologists</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-emerald-700 text-3xl">Philosophy of Care</h2>
				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">“I believe in clear communication, rapid diagnosis and minimally-invasive treatments that allow patients to return to full function sooner. Every scan and procedure is tailored to the individual's clinical question.”</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="mb-4 font-semibold text-emerald-700 text-3xl">Research &amp; Teaching</h2>
				<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Dr&nbsp;Purohit's research interests include novel injectable therapies for osteoarthritis and tendon pathology. He is a course faculty member for the RCR MSK ultrasound workshops and supervises radiology trainees on fellowship programmes.</p>
			</section>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>